{
  "text": "For most authors,\u00af1 is interpreted as an estimate of barriers to trade, although some (e.g., [CITATION_1] ) also consider this coe\u00b1cient as an estimate of search costs. According to the functional form in (6) , the elasticity of bilateral trade with respect to distance,\u00aft, is given by:",
  "correct_citation": {
